  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The goal of the project is to test and monitor two NOVEA pumps in different environments in Pakistan. These pumps require less maintenance than the existing ones and facilitate local maintenance at the community level. The aim of this project is to assess these pumps and conduct a field test in order to: demonstrate the reliability of the technology by providing a safe and sustainable water supply to the communities and increase the implication of the users</narrative>
  </description>
